pr_title: pclmtoraster: Completed implementation of remaining features
pr_body:
The following features have been added.
1. Support for banded and planar rasters and support for conversion of bits.
2. Support for Duplex printing
3. Margins and page sizes would be matched from ppd (just as in pdftoraster with slight modifications).
4. Support for bi-level output rasters.

Test reports are available [here](https://github.com/V1krant/test-report). (Size ~500 mb).

pr_title: Add support for colorspace conversions in pclmtoraster filter
pr_body:
Support for colorspace conversions has been added for pclm and raster pdfs with `DeviceRGB`, `DeviceCMYK`, and `DeviceGray` colorspaces.
Test reports can be found [here](https://github.com/V1krant/test-reports).

I have added the new `pclmtoraster` which converts `pclm` files to raster. Currently the following colorspaces are tested and supported :
cmyk, rgb, srgb, adobergb, black (1 Bit), and sgray.
Currently, conversion from one colorspace to another is not supported.
Some test reports are available [here](https://github.com/V1krant/test-reports).
